SLING
========
SLING    is powerful  Programming Language invented    in  WEB  by  wilmix jemin  j for  Remotewebappplication at  year  2016.





SLING   is  focused   on modules  which  are


a)  ERP  => BSTAR

b)  CRM => CSTAR

c) ECOMMERCE => ESTAR

D)  Advanced Business=> SDOLLAR
